WEBVTT

00:00.966 --> 00:02.867
<i>Previously on Transformers Prime...</i>

00:02.869 --> 00:07.572
<i>The specimen you see
before you was bred in the laboratory,</i>

00:07.574 --> 00:10.875
<i>cloned from fossilized remains,
which I discovered on Cybertron.</i>

00:10.877 --> 00:14.212
A dragon?
Where'd the 'Cons get a dragon?!

00:18.017 --> 00:19.884
<i>Ultra Magnus?</i>

00:19.886 --> 00:22.812
- It's an honor.
- "It's an honor, Sir."

00:23.056 --> 00:27.358
<i>We must stop Megatron.
With or without Optimus Prime.</i>

00:27.360 --> 00:32.563
- Who put shoulderpads in command?
- Ultra Magnus is the only logical choice.

00:32.564 --> 00:37.568
- Optimus! I have the forge!
- Whatever power remains...

00:37.570 --> 00:41.706
must be used to restore Cybertron.

00:41.708 --> 00:47.778
<i>The time for a new leader
is upon us.</i>

00:47.780 --> 00:50.628
I believe that leader...

00:50.629 --> 00:54.707
stands before me right now.

00:58.690 --> 01:02.026
<i>Autobots.
We remain vastly outnumbered,</i>

01:02.028 --> 01:05.930
and, despite our munitions,
do not currently possess the firepower

01:05.932 --> 01:09.767
necessary to compromise
the Decepticon citadel.

01:09.769 --> 01:12.803
Uncle Sam's military does.
I just can't let them make a move

01:12.805 --> 01:16.107
as long as Megatron's ray
guns are pointed at Washington.

01:16.109 --> 01:17.575
Then we must infiltrate Darkmount

01:17.577 --> 01:19.977
in order to nullify its fusion cannons.

01:19.979 --> 01:23.681
Unfortunately, it seems the
fortress is heavily shielded

01:23.683 --> 01:25.449
against unauthorized groundbridges.

01:25.451 --> 01:28.719
Even those originating
from Decepticon technology.

01:28.721 --> 01:33.090
Guess we'll have to sneak past
enemy lines. Wrecker-style.

01:33.092 --> 01:36.927
I couldn't deal with
"Wrecker-style" back on Cybertron,

01:36.929 --> 01:40.030
and I refuse to deal with it here.

01:40.032 --> 01:41.098
Hmm.

01:41.100 --> 01:43.518
Now, we require a means of thinning

01:43.519 --> 01:45.936
the Decepticon ranks to even the odds,

01:45.938 --> 01:49.907
If we're to have any hope
of completing this mission.

01:49.909 --> 01:51.008
Or of surviving it.

01:56.147 --> 01:59.276
